name: Happy but Empty
description:
Inner emptiness is caused by a lack of love, When we don’t love yourself, ignore feelings, and always try to get attention and approval from others, we can experience feeling empty.

All people are creative and full of potential, but not all of them use this potential and, thus, feel as though they’re wasting their time and energy. And I try to fill the void with food, relationships, work, and things that are supposed to distract attention.
